title: Kaley Cuoco’s ex wants spousal support
text:
Kaley Cuoco’s ex wants spousal support Staff Writers AAP Kaley Cuoco’s ex wants spousal support Staff Writers AAP Will the Big Bang star have to pay big bucks? 
ACTRESS Kaley Cuoco’s estranged husband Ryan Sweeting is reportedly requesting spousal support despite signing a prenuptial. 
The Big Bang Theory star, 29, announced in September she was divorcing the professional tennis player after less than two years of marriage. 
Her divorce documents revealed the couple had signed a prenuptial agreement, but on Monday, Ryan submitted his own papers requesting spousal support from his wife, according to ET Online. 
While Cuoco has amassed a fortune of approximately $US45 million ($A62.05 million), Ryan, 28, has a net worth $US2 million. 
Ryan’s paperwork also cites a different date of separation to the one his estranged spouse offered. 
Cuoco noted September 3 as the date they split, while the sportsman listed September 25 as the day the couple decided to dissolve their marriage. Other Stories
